    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《一线生机》是一款边抢地盘边搞基建的回合制策略游戏。这回咱不演勇者了——直接当全大陆最让人腿软的硬茬：兽人！老家经济已崩，战争首领放话：“不惜一切搞钱，重振部落雄风！”形势迫人，赶紧支棱起来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322260/extras/66ab90c8777a5635c615a9c3f52effda.avif?t=1771680395\" width=1170 height=427 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322260/extras/4fc5cf4919d308e891e46086d346c779.webp?t=1771680395\" width=421 height=31 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">兽人哪有那么容易嘎？他们只会越挨打越上头！脸接大招、资源被偷、一回合砍嗨了……全都能让兽人怒气值爆表。东西抢够了？眼看小弟们眼冒红光、集体吼出“一个不留！”时——风紧扯呼才是真智慧！万一全员同时暴走，本次抢劫连人带货直接白给。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322260/extras/cb987d7c474f3ec5e7ed1049608dfe00.poster.avif?t=1771680395\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322260/extras/cb987d7c474f3ec5e7ed1049608dfe00.webm?t=1771680395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322260/extras/cb987d7c474f3ec5e7ed1049608dfe00.mp4?t=1771680395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322260/extras/0606913f3fac1762a96d1a55d8eb90d4.webp?t=1771680395\" width=279 height=32 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">掠夺任务直接空投到随机生成的地图，带着兄弟自由乱逛，随时可能撞见奇葩NPC、神秘宝藏、隐藏剧情和阴间对手。刚被提拔成大酋长的你，接到首领的硬核指标：冲进不同地貌疯抢资源，能薅多少薅多少！但千万绷住一根弦：咱是来发财的，不是来灭门的！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322260/extras/c8a84d8f78a217d6c7f9ddf5062b8410.poster.avif?t=1771680395\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322260/extras/c8a84d8f78a217d6c7f9ddf5062b8410.webm?t=1771680395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322260/extras/c8a84d8f78a217d6c7f9ddf5062b8410.mp4?t=1771680395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322260/extras/2651140adc2e1297856197930b7e4b64.webp?t=1771680395\" width=343 height=32 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">让破营地焕发第二春！盖作坊、起高墙、整点花里胡哨的装饰——不仅能给兽人加战力加Buff，还能挑战更狠的副本，搬回更肥的油水。打造独家神装，穿搭全靠你定义。偶尔还有NPC上门交易、送你图纸，甚至找你摸鱼唠嗑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322260/extras/c78bf253ad40c2e9b6fc2da15c96cc59.poster.avif?t=1771680395\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322260/extras/c78bf253ad40c2e9b6fc2da15c96cc59.webm?t=1771680395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322260/extras/c78bf253ad40c2e9b6fc2da15c96cc59.mp4?t=1771680395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322260/extras/4d3120daa4c14271fcf73f5688e7faba.webp?t=1771680395\" width=253 height=32 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">别以为兽人只会打架！这届小弟内心戏多着呢：有梦想、会emo、还会突发奇想。引导他们培养战友情（嗑CP搞团建）、点亮神奇技能树（烹饪种菜甚至瑜伽），再拿捏各自脾气——助每位兽人成长为不一样的烟火！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322260/extras/17bdf94ecd9f62a49f30b9b60a126309.poster.avif?t=1771680395\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322260/extras/17bdf94ecd9f62a49f30b9b60a126309.webm?t=1771680395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322260/extras/17bdf94ecd9f62a49f30b9b60a126309.mp4?t=1771680395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 兽人真心不莽夫：这回咱当大陆食物链顶端的恐怖存在</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 地图随机花样多：走着走着就撞上财神爷/扫把星</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 我的部落我做主：为排面与实力疯狂基建+穿搭</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 手绘狂躁风格拉满：每一笔都透着“我很怒但我很帅”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 最后嘶吼一遍核心纲领：咱们是来搞钱的——别、全、杀、光！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
